These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, punk, blues, house
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of blues and the fan of house##2
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of folk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | folk | house | punk | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, lemonade, tea
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | tea | juice | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, goat, fish, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the rabbit##2
3. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | snake | rabbit | fish | goat |

